<plot>The making of Alien: Resurrection (1997) is covered in this feature-length documentary, created for the film's 2003 DVD release. The cast and crew tell us how this movie came to be, from it's script which never changed through production, to its initial theatrical release.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412658</url></doc>
